  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/145524e2106c5284e34ce0b24085c3ac.webp?t=1748644919\" width=600 height=60 /></span><strong>Cat's Vote</strong> is a resource management and decision-making simulation where every choice counts. As the head of a feline household, you must ensure your family's happiness by meeting their needs—whether it's electricity/water bills, food, or entertainment. But there's a twist: the price of resources fluctuates based on the decisions of a cat government, and you get to cast your vote in the elections!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/761d3483e779ac931e0e595070f0c106.webp?t=1748644919\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/bb0ecdcebb2546643a5a54e5018f06f7.poster.avif?t=1748644919\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/bb0ecdcebb2546643a5a54e5018f06f7.webm?t=1748644919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/bb0ecdcebb2546643a5a54e5018f06f7.mp4?t=1748644919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Balance your limited budget</strong>, make strategic votes, and keep your family satisfied, all while navigating the unpredictable landscape of feline politics. Will you thrive, or will the promises made by smooth-talking candidates lead your family into ruin?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/6e4cbbfc2b595fafe10449008bfb6746.webp?t=1748644919\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/2586caf3bcb5bc203cc4ed9710ab4f71.poster.avif?t=1748644919\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/2586caf3bcb5bc203cc4ed9710ab4f71.webm?t=1748644919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/2586caf3bcb5bc203cc4ed9710ab4f71.mp4?t=1748644919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Every election season</strong>, you'll hear promises from candidates claiming they will reduce costs or improve living conditions, but can you trust them? Choose wisely, as the wrong decision could send prices soaring and your family into disarray. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/3d84b96974fa2be891db7046bc231a40.poster.avif?t=1748644919\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/3d84b96974fa2be891db7046bc231a40.webm?t=1748644919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/3d84b96974fa2be891db7046bc231a40.mp4?t=1748644919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/9af97c824292c9ba3cccbea5083643d0.webp?t=1748644919\" width=600 height=60 /></span><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 <strong>Resource Management</strong>: Stretch your budget to provide for your cat family’s needs—every bill counts.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗳️ <strong>Feline Elections</strong>: Vote in elections where candidates’ promises directly impact the cost of living. Will they stay true to their word?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌈 <strong>Pastel Charm</strong>: Enjoy a world brought to life with soft pastel hues and a cozy, inviting art style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐱 <strong>Customizable Cats</strong>: Randomize and name your adorable feline family members for a unique experience every time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔄 <strong>Dynamic Gameplay</strong>: No two games are the same—new elections, new promises, new challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎭 <strong>Multiple Endings</strong>: Shape the outcome of your cat family’s story based on the decisions you make and the votes you cast.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/bb277999faac082234c98843c2f8073e.poster.avif?t=1748644919\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/bb277999faac082234c98843c2f8073e.webm?t=1748644919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/bb277999faac082234c98843c2f8073e.mp4?t=1748644919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you lead your cat family to a bright future, or will you fall for the empty promises of politicians? Find out in <i>Cat's Vote</i>—where every decision truly matters.</p>",
