></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 <strong>Resource Management</strong>: Stretch your budget to provide for your cat family’s needs—every bill counts.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗳️ <strong>Feline Elections</strong>: Vote in elections where candidates’ promises directly impact the cost of living. Will they stay true to their word?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌈 <strong>Pastel Charm</strong>: Enjoy a world brought to life with soft pastel hues and a cozy, inviting art style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐱 <strong>Customizable Cats</strong>: Randomize and name your adorable feline family members for a unique experience every time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔄 <strong>Dynamic Gameplay</strong>: No two games are the same—new elections, new promises, new challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎭 <strong>Multiple Endings</strong>: Shape the outcome of your cat family’s story based on the decisions you make and the votes you cast.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/bb277999faac082234c98843c2f8073e.poster.avif?t=1748644919\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/bb277999faac082234c98843c2f8073e.webm?t=1748644919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632940/extras/bb277999faac082234c98843c2f8073e.mp4?t=1748644919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you lead your cat family to a bright future, or will you fall for the empty promises of politicians? Find out in <i>Cat's Vote</i>—where every decision truly matters.</p>",
